# analysis-data/ IS tracked (small, curated re-run data -- see workflows/scaling/analysis-data/
# README.md), but defensively ignore anything bulky/sensitive that should never land there even
# by accident (out/ above already blocks the source of these entirely; this is belt-and-suspenders
# in case someone copies the wrong thing straight into analysis-data/).
workflows/scaling/analysis-data/**/pq/
workflows/scaling/analysis-data/**/*.sif
workflows/scaling/analysis-data/**/*_logs/
workflows/scaling/analysis-data/**/slurm_logs/
workflows/scaling/analysis-data/**/run_logs/
